valid rule objects. The use of a fixed `RULE_ORDER` ensures predictable behavior.\n\n## Issues Found\nNo issues were found.\n\n## Verdict: PASS\n\n## Notes for Lead Agent\nThe framework is well-built and ready for concrete rule implementations. The `quantity_overrides` mechanism in `apply()` provides the necessary hook for the \"authoring surface\" mentioned in the requirements.\n"}}
