sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/prd-snapshot.md:15:**Public-facing target:** `cypherclaw.holdenu.com` (Cloudflare-fronted, R2 storage, Worker for routing/HLS)
sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/prd-snapshot.md:22:CypherClaw is an autonomous music-making entity that has been running continuously for ~12 days at the time of this PRD, composing through a SuperCollider-driven duet composer with seven voices (pluck, breath, choir, kotekan, pad, bowed, tabla_tin) across scenes whose arc phases cycle Listen / Conversation / Divination / Procession. It currently outputs through one master reverb on a JACK graph and is heard only inside the room where the box lives.
sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/prd-snapshot.md:45:- Real `jackd` on `hw:USB` Scarlett (PID 1337) — not the PipeWire-JACK shim
sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/prd-snapshot.md:71:- JACK only. `jack_rec` exists for recording to disk.
sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/prd-snapshot.md:85:- Cloudflare Worker (TypeScript) at `worker/` with `wrangler.toml`, handles `/api/*` for `explorer.holdenu.com`
sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/prd-snapshot.md:86:- R2 bucket for audio storage with byte-range proxy via `GET /api/stream/:trackId`
sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/prd-snapshot.md:88:- No `cypherclaw.holdenu.com` subdomain exists yet — Cloudflare DNS + Worker route needed
sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/prd-snapshot.md:121:- **Approve cost-bearing changes** — anything that would incur new Cloudflare Worker billing (currently free tier), R2 storage spend, or external compute. PRD anticipates staying within free tiers; if a feature requires paid services, escalate.
sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/prd-snapshot.md:122:- **Approve credential changes** — Cloudflare API tokens for `cypherclaw.holdenu.com` DNS, R2 access for upload.
sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/prd-snapshot.md:189:- **Encoding (on cypherclaw):** `audio_streamer.py` daemon subscribes to JACK output bus, runs Opus encoding via `pyogg` or shells `opusenc`/`ffmpeg`. Produces 6-second Opus segments at ~96 kbps. Each segment HTTP-POSTed to the Cloudflare Worker.
sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/prd-snapshot.md:190:- **Segment/playlist management (Cloudflare Worker, extends existing holdenu-api worker):**
sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/prd-snapshot.md:191:  - `POST /api/cypherclaw/segment` — receives a binary segment + metadata header (sequence number, duration, current scene, current tuning). Stores in R2 under `cypherclaw/live/{YYYY-MM-DD}/seg-{seq}.opus`. Updates `live.m3u8` HLS playlist (last ~10 segments).
sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/prd-snapshot.md:192:  - `GET /api/cypherclaw/live.m3u8` — serves current playlist (no auth).
sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/prd-snapshot.md:193:  - `GET /api/cypherclaw/segment/{path}` — serves segment from R2 with byte-range support.
sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/prd-snapshot.md:194:  - `GET /api/cypherclaw/live-features` — Server-Sent Events stream of live audio features + scene metadata + current tuning. cypherclaw POSTs periodically to a feature-update endpoint; Worker fans out via Durable Object.
sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/prd-snapshot.md:197:- **Session archival:** When the composer transitions out of a long "session" (definition TBD by engineering; suggest: a continuous span >= 8 minutes with reasonable rms variance), `session_archiver.py` selects representative segments, concatenates into a single Opus file, computes the title per CypherClaw's pattern (`{House-Imagery} / {Tuning-Character} — {DD Month}`), uploads to R2 under `cypherclaw/archive/{session_id}/`, and records metadata.
sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/prd-snapshot.md:198:- **Page (`cypherclaw.holdenu.com`):** Static page served by Cloudflare Worker or Pages. HTML structure:
sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/prd-snapshot.md:199:  - `<audio>` element pointing at `live.m3u8` (hls.js polyfill for non-Safari browsers)
sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/prd-snapshot.md:203:- **DNS / TLS:** New Cloudflare DNS A/AAAA records for `cypherclaw.holdenu.com` → Worker route. Reuse existing Cloudflare zone.
sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/prd-snapshot.md:207:- `my-claw/tools/audio_streamer.py` (Opus encoder + HTTP poster)
sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/prd-snapshot.md:209:- `catalog-explorer/worker/src/cypherclaw.ts` (new Worker module for cypherclaw routes)
sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/prd-snapshot.md:216:- `catalog-explorer/worker/wrangler.toml` (R2 bindings, route for cypherclaw.holdenu.com)
