g by callers.\n\n## Issues Found\n- [x] (Resolved) Mandatory hardening checks for `bootstrap_identity` were verified as pre-existing and correctly wired in the daemon startup flow.\n\n## Verdict: PASS\n\n## Notes for Lead Agent\nThe implementation is solid and satisfies all requirements for T-022 Zc. The integration with the existing tracker and journal persistence layers is seamless. The hardening anchors for startup identity were also verified as passing.\n","file_path":"sdp/verification/t-022 @20260425t183959zc-verify.md"}}
